        "",
        "Formula:  Conv = POSITIVES − FADE SUBTRACTIONS, then clamped to 0–100.",
        "Sort: Conv descending, then HR probability.   Row color: gold ≥45 · amber ≥34 · blue ≥24 · grey below.",
        "",
        "HIGHEST ACHIEVABLE = 100 (hard clamp). The positives can only sum past 100 if an implausible",
